Bash(__NEW_LINE_862c47c1bb9963eb__ psql "$DATABASE_URL" -c "
SELECT table_name, 
       \(SELECT COUNT\(*\) FROM information_schema.columns c 
        WHERE c.table_name = t.table_name AND c.table_schema = ''landscape''\) as column_count
FROM information_schema.tables t
WHERE table_schema = ''landscape'' 
AND \(
    table_name ILIKE ''%expense%'' 
    OR table_name ILIKE ''%opex%'' 
    OR table_name ILIKE ''%cost%''
    OR table_name ILIKE ''%budget%''
    OR table_name ILIKE ''%category%''
    OR table_name ILIKE ''%fee%''
    OR table_name ILIKE ''%capex%''
    OR table_name ILIKE ''%capital%''
    OR table_name ILIKE ''%acquisition%''
    OR table_name ILIKE ''%construction%''
    OR table_name ILIKE ''%development%''
    OR table_name ILIKE ''%infrastructure%''
    OR table_name ILIKE ''%professional%''
    OR table_name ILIKE ''%finance%''
    OR table_name ILIKE ''%fin_%''
    OR table_name ILIKE ''%core_fin%''
\)
ORDER BY table_name;
")

Bash(__NEW_LINE_3e92759ba6fa159d__ psql "$DATABASE_URL" -c "
COPY \(
SELECT 
  c.category_id,
  c.category_name,
  c.account_number,
  c.parent_id,
  p.category_name as parent_name,
  array_agg\(DISTINCT ls.activity\) as lifecycle_stages,
  c.property_types,
  c.tags
FROM landscape.core_unit_cost_category c
LEFT JOIN landscape.core_unit_cost_category p ON c.parent_id = p.category_id
LEFT JOIN landscape.core_category_lifecycle_stages ls ON c.category_id = ls.category_id
GROUP BY c.category_id, c.category_name, c.account_number, c.parent_id, p.category_name, c.property_types, c.tags
ORDER BY c.account_number, c.category_name
\) TO STDOUT WITH CSV HEADER")
